data.text:
As I mentioned quite some time ago, I’m cleaning house in an attempt to make some room. These are all from my personal collection and have been well taken care of.

I’m asking $5 per cd, $3 per single, $7 per double cd and $10 for each bootleg (all listed are original silver versions). If you buy less than 10 items, you pay the actual shipping cost. Anything 10 or over and I’ll pay for shipping.

This is intended to clean up some major space, so I’ll be tossing in some bonus things that I’ve got laying around. The more you buy, the more and better quality stuff I’ll throw in. Could be anything from burned copies of bootlegs that may or may not be in circulation, some bootleg Russian mp3 collections I picked up back in the very early 2000s, demos that bands sent me over the years, etc. I’m finding stuff I literally forgot about owning, which is saying a lot for me.

Formatting on this list probably didn’t come out perfectly, so I’ve posted it online here as well: http://www.prongs.org/~bisquitodoom/cdsale.html Let me know if you have any questions, etc.
